Mercantil Servicios Financieros CA (MVZ/A) 
headed to a five-year high in Caracas trading.  Class A shares of Mercantil, a Caracas-based holding
company that offers banking and financial services, climbed 14
percent to 48 bolivars, the highest price since January 2007.
The one-day advance was the biggest since January 2010.  is the biggest since January 2010.  To contact the reporter on this story:
